results.description: Alex & Outlaw are hired to steal the Punisher's guns

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Three
results.description: Alex and Outlaw battle some jewelry thieves.  Taskmaster leaves Sandi.  Mary Zero is introduced

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Four
results.description: Alex is shot and his theme park is burned.  Taskmaster sees Higashi asking Sandi out.

results.title: Dead Man's Switch Part Five
